app.controllers

Class ActionController

  • java.lang.Object
    • app.controllers.ActionController

  • public class ActionController
extends java.lang.Object
    Class ActionController This class takes in a command object, which specifies the details of the action to be carried out, and then interacts with the model through ModelManager to carry out the action. The data structure can then be extracted from this class by the CommandController.
    Author:
    ryan
